      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not a symptom though. it's just clarity. i've spent years chasing this and now that it's gone, i realize how much energy i wasted on something that doesn't matter. it's like the noise finally stopped. instead of trying to climb back up that ladder only to fall again, wouldn't it just be more logical to just stop trying? to just let go?",
